text: Gladkikh () is a rural locality (a village) in Metelinsky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 12 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 77 km from Mesyagutovo, 2 km from Meteli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Gladkikh
